.TH LOOTSHEET-REPORT-WRITEOFF-CANDIDATES 1 "Mar 2026" "LootSheet" "LootSheet Manual"
.SH NAME
lootsheet-report-writeoff-candidates \\- Show stale outstanding quest balances
.SH SYNOPSIS
lootsheet report writeoff-candidates [flags]
.SH DESCRIPTION
LootSheet CLI

Usage:
  lootsheet report writeoff-candidates [--as-of YYYY-MM-DD] [--min-age-days N]

Defaults:
  --as-of         today
  --min-age-days  30

Examples:
  lootsheet report writeoff-candidates
  lootsheet report writeoff-candidates --as-of 2026-04-01 --min-age-days 45
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
--as-of=string
report date in YYYY-MM-DD (default: 2026-03-08)
.TP
-h, --help
help for writeoff-candidates
.TP
--min-age-days=int
minimum completed age in days (default: 30)
.SH SEE ALSO
lootsheet-report(1)
